==Getting the key==
* '''Gunnjorn:''' Haha welcome to my obstacle course. Have fun, but remember this isn't a child's playground. People have died here.
* '''Player:''' Hi, are you called Gunnjorn?
* '''Gunnjorn:''' Why, indeed I am. I own this agility course, it can be very dangerous!
* '''Player:''' Yeah, that's great. Anyway, I understand you have a cousin named Larrissa who gave you a key...?
* '''Gunnjorn:''' Yes, she did! How do you know of this? She said she probably wouldn't need it, but gave it to me for safe keeping just in case.
* '''Player:''' Well, something has happened at the lighthouse, and she has been locked out. I need you to give me her key.
* {{tact|With a full inventory:}}
** '''Gunnjorn:''' Well, I would give you the key, but apparently you don't have any room.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tact|With open inventory spaces:}}
** '''Gunnjorn:''' Sure. Here you go.
** {{tact|end}}

===After obtaining the key===
* '''Gunnjorn:''' Welcome again to my obstacle course. Have fun, but remember this isn't a child's playground. People have died here.
* '''Player:''' Hello again, Gunnjorn. I'm afraid I've lost that key you gave me.
* {{tact|With a full inventory:}}
** '''Gunnjorn:''' Well, I would give you another, but apparently you don't have any room.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tact|With open inventory spaces:}}
** '''Gunnjorn:''' No problem. Here you go.
** {{tact|end}}

