* '''Larrissa:''' What can have happened here? Please, you must fix the light, we cannot let my darling Jossik take the blame for any shipwrecks!
* '''Player:''' Okay, I will see what I can do.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Larrissa again===
* '''Player:''' What am I supposed to be doing again?
* '''Larrissa:''' You MUST find a way to fix the lighthouse! The ships are in terrible danger as long as the light is not working properly!
* '''Player:''' Do you have any idea how I could do that?
* '''Larrissa:''' I'm sorry adventurer, I do not know anything about lighthouses.
* '''Larrissa:''' I'm sure there must be some kind of user's guide around here somewhere though.
* '''Larrissa:''' My darling Jossik knew nothing about Lighthouses when he first came here, so the council must have left him some kind of manual or something.
* {{tact|end}}

