==Talking to Jossik in the basement==
* '''Jossik:''' *cough* Please... please help me... I think my leg is broken, and those creatures will be back any minute now!
* '''Player:''' I guess you're Jossik then... What creatures are you talking about?
* '''Jossik:''' I... I do not know. I have never seen their like before!
* '''Jossik:''' I was searching for information about my uncle Silas, who vanished mysteriously from this lighthouse many months ago. I found the secret of that strange wall, and discovered that I could use it as a door, but when I
* '''Jossik:''' came down here I was attacked by...
* '''Jossik:''' Well, I do not know what they are, but they are very strong! They hurt me badly enough to trap me here, and I have been fearing for my life ever since!
* '''Player:''' Don't worry, I'm here now. Larrissa was worried about you and asked for my help.
* '''Player:''' I'll go back upstairs and let her know that I've found you and that you're still alive, and then we can work out some way of getting you out of here, okay?
* '''Jossik:''' NO! No, you can't leave me now! Look! They're coming again! Do something!
* {{qact|A dagannoth appears and attacks the player.}}

==Upon killing the dagannoth or talking to Jossik==
* '''Jossik:''' NO! No, you can't leave me now! Look! They're coming again! Do something!
* '''Player:''' Okay, now that the creature's dead we can get you out of here.
* '''Jossik:''' No... you do not understand...
* '''Jossik:''' That was not the creature that attacked me...
* '''Jossik:''' That was one of its babies...
* {{qact|The dagannoth mother appears and attacks the player.}}

===Talking to Larrissa after killing the dagannoth===
* '''Player:''' I found Jossik! He's in a cavern underground...
* '''Larrissa:''' That is wonderful news! But why does he not come up out of there?
* '''Player:''' Um... well, there's a big monster down there with him stopping him leaving.
* '''Larrissa:''' What?!?! You MUST save him! I beseech you, please! Do something!
* '''Player:''' Okay, okay, sheesh, keep your hair on...
* {{tact|end}}

